---
layout: layout.njk
title: Galerie
description: Bilder des Astris Trio aus Konzerten und Fotoshootings
---

<section class="editorial">
  <div class="editorial__header">
    <h1 class="editorial__title">Galerie</h1>
    <p class="editorial__lead">
      Eindrücke aus Konzerten, Proben und Fotoshootings des Astris Trio.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="gallery">
    {% for image in gallery %}
      <figure class="gallery__item">
        <img
          src="{{ image.src }}"
          alt="{{ image.alt }}"
          loading="lazy"
          class="gallery__image"
        >
        {% if image.caption %}
          <figcaption class="gallery__caption">{{ image.caption }}</figcaption>
        {% endif %}
      </figure>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
</section>
